表演</a>。</p><p>与此同时，《Jane&#39;s Addiction》已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-future-islands-and-more-for-bearded-theory-2024-buy-tickets-3527883">宣布成为 Bearded Theory 2024 的头条新闻，并在英国独家演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-share-new-single-little-me-ahead-of-farewell-tour-3581475">Porno For Pyros 在告别巡演前分享新单曲《Little Me》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
